transparent_hr_bot

educational tool on RAG
explains the process and shows output
exposes the chunking and retrieval process
logs the query and answer evalutation
logs when it encounters a question it cannot answer

value
- allows creator to understand what happens behind the scene
- understand how the llm understands your document
- exposes what the bot can answer and cannot
- allows you to modify your source document and select the understanding method 

Look into llm project to see how llm calls are structured